review_data: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2020
name: Michael D. Frericks
title: Excellent Yogurt
review: Made the yogurt to have enough to do a massive batch and then 2 nights later I make the baked milk yogurt which came out awesome. I could have cooked it a bit longer and will next time. If you like yogurt you need to try Russian Baked Yogurt...really good.
